<div id="pf421e" class="pf w53 h2f4" data-page-no="421e"><div class="pc pc421e w53 h2f4"><div class="t m8d x71 h5 y2c1c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 8 May 14-20 </div><div class="t m121 x71 h35 y2a47 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these things possibly be? </div><div class="t ma7 x48 h35 y29f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">And how it would please the evil one </div><div class="t m156f x71 h35 y2bff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to see us in contention over the </div><div class="t m7b3 x71 h35 y2446 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">manner in which our Saviour saves us, </div><div class="t m80e x71 h35 y222c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to see us in argument and debate over </div><div class="t m7c9 x71 h35 y1036 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how these things can be! We may not </div><div class="t mf3c x71 h35 ydf1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">know exactly how these things can be. </div><div class="t m1d2 x71 h35 yfdf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We may not need to know exactly how </div><div class="t mb7f x71 h35 y1208 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">these things can be. There is no </div><div class="t m8bb x71 h35 y921 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">legitimate reason for strife and debate </div><div class="t m71d x71 h35 y125f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">over the manner in which the Lord </div><div class="t m1d1 x71 h35 yec1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">would redeem His children. The vital </div><div class="t mac5 x71 h35 yd53 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">question is, Are we ready to be </div><div class="t ma54 x71 h35 ydc6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">redeemed? Are we willing to be born </div><div class="t m6e9 x71 h35 yc6b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">again? Are we prepared to be placed </div><div class="t m723 x71 h35 yddc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">entirely under new management? Are </div><div class="t m66 x71 h35 y1025 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we prepared to surrender the reins </div><div class="t m878 x71 h35 ya8b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that govern the direction of our </div><div class="t m8b3 x71 h35 y1834 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thoughts and affections? If not, our </div><div class="t me4e x71 h35 y83c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">independence may cost us eternal life. </div><div class="t m3d0 x73 h35 yd57 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Shortly after the 1888 General </div><div class="t m84c x71 h35 y958 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference session in Minneapolis, </div><div class="t m234 x71 h35 y109c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there was a minister among us who </div><div class="t maea x71 h35 y92e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was very certain that his ideas on </div><div class="t m62a x71 h35 y9f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">things were the correct ideas, and that </div><div class="t m5a9 x71 h35 y101a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only those who saw things as he saw </div><div class="t ma11 x71 h35 yec9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them were walking in the light. The </div><div class="t m194 x71 h35 yf06 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rest he believed were walking in </div><div class="t ma73 x71 h35 ybb7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">darkness, and especially the ministers. </div><div class="t m6b6 x71 h35 y7d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He wanted to stand out, to be </div><div class="t m9ad x26 h35 ya95 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">different. In his egotism he insisted </div><div class="t m398 x71 h35 y74a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that others should see things as he did </div><div class="t m2aa x71 h35 yadf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">or they could not be saved. </div><div class="t m39c x73 h35 y4b3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The servant of the Lord wrote a </div><div class="t m6c1 x26 h35 yd60 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lengthy letter to this brother and </div><div class="t m1119 x26 h35 y203a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">repeatedlypointed out to him his </div><div class="t mb48 x26 h35 y12bf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">danger in dwelling upon certain </div><div class="t m114 x26 h35 y7df ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">subjects, certain ideas, in which he felt </div><div class="t ma8b x26 h35 y14af ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he was far out in front of almost </div><div class="t m48d x26 h35 yd80 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">everybody else. The Lord&apos;s messenger </div><div class="t md06 x26 h35 y47c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">went so far as to indicate that at times </div><div class="t m8d9 x26 h35 ye6b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this man&apos;s mind was &quot;unbalanced </div><div class="t m110b x26 h35 y101d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">from trying very hard to study into and </div><div class="t m2bc x26 h35 yffc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">explain the mystery of godliness, </div><div class="t m98e x26 h35 yd2b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which isjlust as great a mystery after </div><div class="t m23c x26 h35 yc0f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">your study and explanations as it was </div><div class="t m14d x26 h35 ye3a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">before.&quot; He was further counseled </div><div class="t m8d9 x26 h35 yd4a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that he was not leaving the Lord </div><div class="t m195a x26 h35 y1152 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enough room to work upon people&apos;s </div><div class="t m813 x26 h35 yc11 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">minds and to speak to their souls and </div><div class="t m9d6 x26 h35 y1f97 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to impress their understanding. In this  </div><div class="t m3cf x4b h35 y2a12 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">setting he was told, &quot;It is not essentia </div><div class="t m6a9 xab h35 y29f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for you to know and tell others all the </div><div class="t m8be xab h35 y23f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whys and wherefores as to what </div><div class="t m241 xab h35 y22f7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">constitutes the new heart, or as to the </div><div class="t m451 xab h35 y222c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">position they can and must reach so as </div><div class="t maf6 xab h35 y1035 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">never to sin. You have no such work tc </div><div class="t m3df xab h35 ydf1 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">do.&quot;—Selected Messages, </div><div class="t m6ca x196 h35 ydf0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bk. 1, p. </div><div class="t m8d xab h35 yfdf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">177. </div><div class="t m70a xa5 h35 y1208 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The reason given that this brother </div><div class="t mbe5 xab h35 y4db ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should not attempt to explain all the </div><div class="t ma3f xab h35 y1272 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whys and wherefores, even of the nevl </div><div class="t m41c xab h35 ybae ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">birth or of the new heart, was the fact </div><div class="t m23a xab h35 yd53 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that &quot;all are not constituted alike. </div><div class="t m17a xab h35 y73c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conversions are not all alike.&quot; </div><div class="t m1be xab h35 yd38 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Different individuals have different </div><div class="t m2ea xab h35 yddc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">experiences in conversion, but no one </div><div class="t m657 xab h35 y1232 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is to judge the conversion of another </div><div class="t m61d xab h35 ya8b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not genuine because the experience is </div><div class="t m4c9 xab h35 y1834 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not exactly like his own. So even in our </div><div class="t mac8 xab h35 yc78 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of this week&apos;s lesson, we may </div><div class="t m411 xab h35 yd57 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not all see it just exactly alike. But what </div><div class="t ma0e xab h35 yc79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we all do need to do is to see Christ </div><div class="t m82f xab h35 y1275 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lifted up. &quot;With outstretched arms He<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t me8b xab h35 yaab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is ready to receive and welcome not </div><div class="t mfab xab h35 y1575 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only the sinner but the prodigal. His </div><div class="t m708 xab h35 yf30 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">dying love, manifested on Calvary, is<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m3cf xab h35 y1075 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the sinner&apos;s assurance of acceptance,<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m98a xab h35 yd24 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">peace, and love. Teach these things in<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m2c8 xab h35 ya49 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the simplest form, that the </div><div class="t m13a xab h35 y7d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sin-darkened soul may see the light </div><div class="t m824 xab h35 ya95 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shining from the cross of </div><div class="t m406 xab h35 yf3e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ca Iva ry.&quot;—,Selected </div><div class="t m759 xcb h35 yf3e ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Messages, </div><div class="t m8f2 x1de h35 yf3e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bk. 1,<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t md9 xab h35 y9bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 178, 179. With that caution and </div><div class="t m840 xab h35 y15aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with that appeal, let us proceed to </div><div class="t m821 xab h35 y15fc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study this vital subject; for without the<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m4a5 xab h35 y864 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">new-birth experience no man shall see<span class="fc0 sc0"> </span></div><div class="t m97c xab h35 y12bf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Lord. </div><div class="t m14a xab h5 y1361 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f xab h5 yd80 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m111e xb3 h5 y1291 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Except&quot; </div><div class="t m754 xb3 h5 y1223 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 3:3) </div><div class="t m558 xab h5 y1239 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m1d0 xb3 h5 yce0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Of Water and of the Spirit&quot; </div><div class="t m754 xb3 h5 yb89 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 3:5) </div><div class="t mb7 xab h5 yffc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m51f xb3 h5 yd9f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">